1
00:00:06,857 --> 00:00:07,890
Ashley!
希礼

2
00:00:15,620 --> 00:00:16,860
Ashley....
希礼

3
00:00:17,497 --> 00:00:18,570
Scarlett.
思嘉

4
00:00:20,020  --> 00:00:22,740
Who are you hiding from in here?
你在这里是想躲谁

5
00:00:27,666 --> 00:00:29,333
What are you up to?
你想做什么

6
00:00:31,342 --> 00:00:34,750
Why aren't you upstairs, resting with the other girls?
你为什么不跟其它女孩 一起在楼上休息呢

7
00:00:35,670 --> 00:00:37,902
What is this, Scarlett, a secret?
怎么回事 思嘉 有秘密吗

8
00:00:38,218 --> 00:00:39,552
Oh, Ashley....
希礼

9
00:00:39,845 --> 00:00:40,928
Ashley!
希礼

10
00:00:41,170 --> 00:00:44,165
-I love you. -Scarlett!
我爱你  思嘉

11
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:46,017
I love you, I do!
我爱你 是真的

12
00:00:47,881 --> 00:00:51,588
Well isn’t it enough that you gathered every other man's heart today?
你今天取得其它所有男人的心 难道还不够吗

13
00:00:51,590 --> 00:00:54,502
You've always had mine. You cut your teeth on it.
我的心一直是你的 上面还留有你的齿痕呢

14
00:00:54,518 --> 00:00:55,230
Don't tease me now.
不要取笑我

15
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:58,902
Have I your heart, my darling? I love you, I love you!
我得到你的心了吗 亲爱的 我爱你 我爱你

16
00:00:58,906 --> 00:01:00,400
Mustn't say such things.
你千万别再说了

17
00:01:00,440  --> 00:01:02,249
You'll hate me for hearing them.
你将会因我听到这些话而恨我

18
00:01:02,259 --> 00:01:06,740
I could never hate you, and I know you must care about me.
我永远都不会恨你的 我也知道你在乎我

19
00:01:06,747 --> 00:01:09,165
Well you do care, don't you?
你在乎的 对吧

20
00:01:10,361 --> 00:01:13,015
Yes, I care.
是的 我在乎

21
00:01:14,622 --> 00:01:17,710
Can't we go away and forget we ever said these things?
我们能不能走开 把说过的话忘了呢 

22
00:01:18,592  --> 00:01:20,843
But how can we do that?
我们怎么能那样呢

23
00:01:21,010 --> 00:01:23,887
Don't you--? Don't you want to marry me?
难道你不想娶我吗

24
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:25,262
I'm going to marry Melanie.
我要娶的是美兰

25
00:01:25,270 --> 00:01:27,824
But you can't! Not if you care for me!
但你不能 如果你在乎我的话

26
00:01:27,830 --> 00:01:31,062
Oh, my dear, why must you make me say things that will hurt you?
天啊 你为什么一定要逼我 说出伤害你的话呢